description: This file is the entry point for a React-based frontend application. It imports necessary modules, including React, ReactDOM, styling, and the main App component, then initializes and renders the root React component within a DOM element with id 'root'.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering React components into a DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree inside the created root.
